Basic application demonstrating Spring Boot / Spring MVC / Thymleaf / REST / Spring Test.

Demonstrates using the Spring Test MockMvc framework for ease of testing controllers.

The back end data is hardcoded in the REST services for this demo.

Unit and integration testing using Springs MockMvc testing framework.

Run with:

mvn spring-boot:run -Drun.jvmArguments="-Xdebug -Xrunjdwp:transport=dt_socket,server=y,suspend=n,address=5005"

(Optionally debug on port 5005).

Navigate to URL:

http://localhost:8080/airport/list